name: Listened to The Year 2 coach check-in + ND game theory

content.html:
After Godfrey unloads some college-centric draft notes, Alex wants to talk about Notre Dame’s upcoming TV negotiation with NBC and how the Big Ten’s new entanglement with the Peacock is a relevant dynamic to keep an eye on. Then, let’s do the year-two vibes check on every head coach hired before the 2022 season. Who’s doing great? Who’s just holding tight? And who has already entered the “better win some games or it could get ugly fast” zone? Production: Anthony Vito.
